		<item>
			<title>FAQ</title>
			<link>http://www.zon.com.tw/zh/20-web/17-faq</link>
			<guid isPermaLink="true">http://www.zon.com.tw/zh/20-web/17-faq</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[<ul>
<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 11.85pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;">
<pre><span style="font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 12pt;" lang="EN-US">How about the quotation?</span></pre>
</li>
<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 11.85pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-outline-level: 2;">
<pre><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 12pt;" lang="EN-US">How many quantities is the minimum order?</span></pre>
</li>
<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 11.85pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-outline-level: 2;">
<pre><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 12pt;" lang="EN-US">How about the packing method? What kind of the packaging does TUNG YI offer?</span></pre>
</li>
<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 11.85pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-outline-level: 2;">
<pre><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 12pt;" lang="EN-US">When is the delivery date?</span></pre>
</li>
<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 11.85pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-outline-level: 2;">
<pre><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 12pt;" lang="EN-US">How about the test strength of the wire cable?</span></pre>
</li>
<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 11.85pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-outline-level: 2;">
<pre><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 12pt;" lang="EN-US">How about the length, size, and color of the wire cable?</span></pre>
</li>
<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 11.85pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-outline-level: 2;">
<pre><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 12pt;" lang="EN-US">Do you have ODM or OEM? How to work ODM or OEM with TUNG YI?</span></pre>
</li>
<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 11.85pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-outline-level: 2;">
<pre><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 12pt;" lang="EN-US">Where is TUNG YI located?</span></pre>
</li>
<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 11.85pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-outline-level: 2;">
<pre><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 12pt;" lang="EN-US">Is it possible for clients who print their logos on the product?</span></pre>
</li>
<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 11.85pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-outline-level: 2;">
<pre><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 12pt;" lang="EN-US">What languages are used to write the instruction manuals?</span></pre>
</li>
<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 11.85pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-outline-level: 2;">
<pre><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 12pt;" lang="EN-US">How does TUNG YI handle defective products?</span></pre>
</li>
<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 11.85pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-outline-level: 2;">
<pre><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 12pt;" lang="EN-US">Can we have an exclusive brand?</span></pre>
</li>
<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 11.85pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-outline-level: 2;">
<pre><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 12pt;" lang="EN-US">How to start a business with TUNG YI?</span></pre>
</li>
<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 11.85pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-outline-level: 2;">
